        <p class="av-section-lead">
          A guided flow that keeps learners focused, while giving mentors clear progress signals.
        </p>
      </div>

      <ol class="av-steps">
        <li class="av-step">
          <span class="av-step-number">1</span>
          <div class="av-step-body">
            <h3 class="av-card-heading">Capture notes with clarity</h3>
            <p>Collect the core ideas you want to retain, then convert them into cards.</p>
          </div>
        </li>

        <li class="av-step">
          <span class="av-step-number">2</span>
          <div class="av-step-body">
            <h3 class="av-card-heading">Study without distractions</h3>
            <p>Focus on one prompt at a time with a smooth, predictable rhythm.</p>
          </div>
        </li>

        <li class="av-step">
