          <div class="av-step-body">
            <h3 class="av-card-heading">Track recall over time</h3>
            <p>Sessions are saved so you always know what needs reinforcement.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </AvContainer>
  </section>

  <section class="av-section">
    <AvContainer size="default">
      <div class="fn-section__header">
        <h2 class="av-section-title">Who uses FlashNote</h2>
        <p class="av-section-lead">
          From classrooms to corporate training, FlashNote fits any learning environment.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="fn-audience-grid">
        <div class="fn-audience">
          <h3>Schools &amp; students</h3>
          <p>Convert lecture notes into quick recall drills.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fn-audience">
          <h3>Coaching institutes</h3>
          <p>Build topic-wise decks for fast revision and test prep.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fn-audience">
          <h3>Teams &amp; HR</h3>
          <p>Train teams on policy, onboarding, and product knowledge.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fn-audience">
          <h3>Self learners</h3>
          <p>Practice personal study plans with consistency and momentum.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </AvContainer>
  </section>

  <section class="av-section">
    <AvContainer size="default">
      <div class="fn-section__header">
        <h2 class="av-section-title">Works with your learning stack</h2>
        <p class="av-section-lead">
          FlashNote is designed to complement other Ansiversa mini apps.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="fn-apps-grid">
        <a
          href="https://quiz.ansiversa.com"
          class="fn-app-card"
        >
          <p class="fn-app-card__label">Assessments</p>
          <h3>Turn assessments into instant flashcards.</h3>
          <p>Import assessment questions and review them until they stick.</p>
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://exam.ansiversa.com"
          class="fn-app-card"
        >
          <p class="fn-app-card__label">Exam Simulator</p>
          <h3>Scale up to timed mock exams.</h3>
          <p>Use flashcards to drill concepts before test day.</p>
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://study-timer.ansiversa.com"
          class="fn-app-card"
        >
          <p class="fn-app-card__label">Study Timer</p>
          <h3>Keep study blocks disciplined.</h3>
          <p>Pair focused sessions with timer-led study cycles.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </AvContainer>
  </section>

  <section class="av-section">
    <AvContainer size="default">
      <div class="fn-section__header">
        <h2 class="av-section-title">Deck sources</h2>
        <p class="av-section-lead">
          Build decks manually or generate with AI. Keep everything organized in one workspace.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="fn-sources-grid">
        <div class="fn-sources-card">
          <p class="fn-sources-card__label">Manual decks</p>
          <p>Create decks from your notes, books, or lectures.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fn-sources-card">
          <p class="fn-sources-card__label">AI generations</p>
          <p>Convert learning content into recall-ready flashcards.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </AvContainer>
  </section>

  <section class="av-section">
    <AvContainer size="default">
      <div class="fn-section__header">
        <h2 class="av-section-title">Built like a system</h2>
        <p class="av-section-lead">
          FlashNote follows the same architecture and governance standards as every Ansiversa mini app.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="fn-proof">
        <div class="fn-proof__item">Deck-first taxonomy with clean owner separation.</div>
        <div class="fn-proof__item">Study sessions saved per user with review history.</div>
        <div class="fn-proof__item">AI generation pipeline for instant deck creation.</div>
      </div>
    </AvContainer>
  </section>

  <section class="av-section fn-final">
    <AvContainer size="default">
      <div class="fn-final__content">
        <div>
          <h2 class="av-section-title">Ready to build your first deck?</h2>
          <p class="av-section-lead">
            Launch FlashNote and start reviewing in minutes.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="fn-final__cta">
          <AvButton href="/decks">Start with FlashNote</AvButton>
        </div>
      </div>
    </AvContainer>
  </section>
</AppShell>

